01:43.136 --> 01:48.342 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ALEX THOMSON: After days of
inevitable speculation based
upon not much, today, something
altogether

01:48.342 --> 01:52.112 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
