10:07.240 --> 10:11.744 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: You talk about
trends. There was, obviously, a
trend towards Republicans in

10:11.744 --> 10:18.485 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
