this initiative.

10:53.253 --> 10:54.320 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Because of the
way it was structured.

10:54.320 --> 10:56.155 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: Because of
the structure of the measure.

