it didn't work out.

11:06.032 --> 11:08.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: It didn't
because the Republicans held
their seats and the Democrats
held their

11:08.668 --> 11:13.940 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
